class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重點唔係想講邊個抄邊個, 只係想問下有冇人都發現呢首歌好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cef7f2cb2ed043add04f12ad8d8f2dbcdb3442f","tid":1818651,"uid":25075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T06:03:58.000Z","msg":"個編曲似<br />\n但係入面都幾唔同下"},{"pid":"2ab1c68bc3752fd26dd4e70637fbcc4c8a32b139","tid":1818651,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T06:05:34.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[全港最大的Fact Check平台-非食店篇]集合超過400間各地區各行業的良心店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1817378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1817378</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a26a8bc61ed7e521c15df5766977b42a705f3209","tid":1818651,"uid":67574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T06:07:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://3cmusic.com/home/hkcopycatreview/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F3cmusic.com%2Fhome%2Fhkcopycatreview%2F&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdMLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=078a1271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://3cmusic.com/home/hkcopycatreview/</a><br />\n<br />\n//那麼，這次要數抄襲事件，做了這麼多年人最令我最感噁心，最感到不可置信的一定是王雙駿給陳奕迅的《我的世界末日》，這是我見過最明目張膽的抄襲事件，更可以完全沒有提過原創者Super Furry Animals的名字或歌曲的名字《Dim Bendith》。而且，《我的世界末日》最令人感到氣憤的地方是，如果你不知道這是一首徹徹底底的抄歌的話，你會真的以為這是一首很出色創新的作品。這就是completely cheating，你以為一個音樂人talented，怎知他原來是倒模照抄？這與情侶偷情沒分別，就是你或者都不會因為他或她偷情而那麼傷心，但當你知道他一直在偷情卻一直在你面前做個好好先生，把你當傻瓜一樣，就是最令人難以接受的cheated感覺。//"},{"pid":"bc69db0cbbec7489edc1cfe3c466731e351e764a","tid":1818651,"uid":85774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T06:11:53.000Z","msg":"多謝樓主 學到野！"},{"pid":"7b32c5d3a24cc70d595c3bb68e5c1443f24c685b","tid":1818651,"uid":308537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T06:12:03.000Z","msg":"見熱門又少咗啲行動po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1818277\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1818277</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區